description: Global X ETF Series - Global X MSCI China ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Mirae Asset Global Investments (Hong Kong) Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of China. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the stocks of large-cap and mid-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of MSCI China Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. Global X ETF Series - Global X MSCI China ETF was formed on June 11, 2013 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: Global X MSCI China ETF (HKD)
